FAQ

Q: Can I use this player on my website to play videos?
A: Yes! This is explicitly permitted.

Q: Can I use this with my own video hosting or CDN?
A: Yes! You can use any hosting service for your media files.

Q: Can I modify the player and use the modified version?
A: Yes! You can customize and modify the player for your own use.

Q: Can I use this in a commercial product?
A: Yes! As long as your product is not a competing media hosting/player service.

Q: Can I create a SaaS video hosting platform using this player?
A: No. Building a media hosting service that offers embeddable players as a
   core feature would be a Competing Use and is prohibited.

Q: What if I need to use this for a competing service?
A: Contact license@fairu.app to discuss alternative licensing arrangements.

Q: Can I contribute to this project?
A: Yes! Contributions are welcome. By contributing, you agree to grant
   Fairu GmbH the rights described in Section 4.
